commit 5d36fca2af0b1ac402bc1bad82eaf6488aa04fb9
Merge: 41f7248 15e3dcf
Author: Benedikt Böhm <bb@xnull.de>
Date:   Tue Jun 25 09:48:24 2013 +0200

    Merge branch 'next'

    This iteration reintroduces vagrant support. To support Zentoo Linux
    base boxes two new plugins have been written for vagrant which need to
    be installed first:

      vagrant plugin install vagrant-systemd
      vagrant plugin install vagrant-zentoo

    To start a Zentoo Linux base image deployed with chef-solo run:

      vagrant up base

    To start a local chef-server that can be used to deploy other vagrant
    VMs on the same network run:

      vagrant up chef

